                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"
                             extent="unknown"
                             resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ማእሰሮሙ፡ <choice>
                           <sic>ወመሸብሮሙ፡</sic>
                        </choice> 
                        ለአጋንንት፡ ወለሰይጣናት፡ በአዊን፡ እሳት፡ በገዲን፡ <supplied reason="omitted">እሳት፡</supplied> በኢጀርታኤል፡ እሳት፡ በአውድታኤል፡ እሳት፡ በብርስበሔል፡ እሳት፡
                     </incipit>
                  </msItem> 
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i3">
                     <locus target="#1a"/>
                     <title>Excerpt from <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1882MarkGo"/> 5:1-13</title>
                     <note>
                        The biblical excerpt is followed by a short invocation to St Mark, which begins as follows: 
                        <q xml:lang="gez">ጸሎቱ፡ ወበረከቱ፡ ለቅዱስ፡ ማርቆስ፡ ይዕቀቦ፡ ለገብሩ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ወያድኅኖ፡ እምሕማመ፡ አጋንንት፡ ወሰይጣናት፡ ለባርያ፡ ወለጌዎን፡</q>. 
                        The name of the owner <persName ref="PRS11696TasfaGi"/> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the beginning of the invocation.
                     </note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i4">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4692MagicPr"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        በስመ፡ አብ፡ <gap reason="omitted"
                             extent="unknown"
                             resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ፍትሐተ፡ ሥራይ፡ ዘኪን፡ ወዘጥበብ፡ 
                        <gap reason="omitted"
                             extent="unknown"
                             resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran"/> ዝንቱ፡ አስማት፡ ዘተቀድሐ፡ እም፹፩መጻሕፍት፡ 
                        <choice>
                           <sic>ወመቃጽርተ፡</sic>
                        </choice> ሐብደረጅን፡ ሐብደረጅን፡ ሐብ<supplied reason="omitted">ደ</supplied>ረጀን፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        በዝንቱ፡ አስማቲከ፡ ፍታሕ<gap reason="lost"/> ወዘርዝር፡ ሠአር፡ ወመንዝ<supplied reason="lost">ር፡</supplied> ኵሎ፡ ሥራየ፡ ወኵሎ፡ አስማተ፡ ዘተደግመ፡ ኀበ፡ ነፍሱ፡ 
                        ወስጋሁ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡ ሰንበቱ።
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName ref="PRS11696TasfaGi"/> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>  
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i5">
