                        ወበስመ፡ ራኮን፡ ራኮን፡ ራኮን፡ አዊን፡ አዊን፡ አዊን፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ይሠአር፡ ሥራያቲሆሙ፡ ወአስማቲሆሙ፡ ለመሠርያን፡ እምላዕለ፡ ገብርከ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName ref="PRS11696TasfaGi"/> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i6">
                     <locus target="#1b"/>
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4623Prayer"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእን<supplied reason="omitted">ት</supplied>፡ ሕማመ፡ ቍርፀት፡ <choice>
                           <sic>ወመገኛ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ወመጋኛ፡</corr>
                        </choice> 
                        በፓኮስ፡ ስምከ፡ በደፌል፡ ስምከ፡ በሕርዮኖስ፡ ስምከ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="gez">
                        ከማሁ፡ አርግዕ፡ ሕማመ፡ ቍርፀት፡ ወ<supplied reason="omitted">መ</supplied>ጋኛ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ተስፋ፡ ጊዮርጊስ፡
                     </explicit>
                     <note>The name of the owner <persName ref="PRS11696TasfaGi"/> is mentioned in the supplication formula at the end of the text.</note>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i7">
                     <title type="complete" ref="LIT4624Prayer"/>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                        ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ሕማመ፡ ውግዓት፡ ምድምድያም፡ ምድምድያስ፡ <choice>
                           <sic>ምድድምያስ፡</sic>
                           <corr resp="PRS4805Grebaut PRS9530Tisseran">ምድምድያስ፡</corr>
                        </choice> 
                        የሃቂ፡ የሀቂ፡ የሃቂ፡
                     </incipit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>       
                  
